  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 64 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - TRUE ROOT CAUSE FIX: reviewStates (from previous game's review session)
    was not cleared in _resetGameUIState(), causing _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations
    to use stale board states from the old game at the same move index —
    producing annotations identical to the old game at that step.
    Fix: _resetGameUIState now clears reviewStates/reviewMode/reviewStep/
    reviewBaseState; _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations gates reviewStates
    shortcut on reviewMode===true (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/game-logic.js: updated export dialog i18n text
    (💾 emoji, "特殊注释"/"special annotations" terminology) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 63 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - Full-chain audit of all [%csl]/[%cal] visual annotation code paths
    confirmed Phase 62 fix is correct.
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: _buildPGNString now accepts
    includeAnnotations parameter (default true); when false, all annotation-
    type tags ([%eval], every-5-moves desc, [%csl]/[%cal]) are omitted;
    new _showPGNExportAnnotationDialog function; copyMoveHistory and
    exportPGNToFile now show the dialog before exporting (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: _pgnCacheSaveCurrent now shows the
    annotation dialog; extracted _pgnCacheSaveCurrentImpl (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/game-logic.js: new i18n keys for export dialog
    (pgn_export_include_annotations_title/msg/yes/no) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

